biweekly.util
Class ICalDateFormatter

java.lang.Object
  biweekly.util.ICalDateFormatter

public class ICalDateFormatter
extends Object

Helper class that formats and parses iCalendar dates. iCalendar dates adhere to the ISO8601 date format standard.

Author:
Michael Angstadt
